N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 22.13 - Superintendent to be notified

State Regulations

Whenever an account of proceedings is to cover a period of
less than 10 years, the superintendent shall be notified at least one month
prior to the close of the accounting period. Notes
